data.description: Welcome to 702 Pointe Circle! This stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath house is a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. This home has been well-kept and is situated in a desirable neighborhood, close to schools, parks and much more! Step inside to a spacious and inviting living area where natural light floods through large windows, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, wood countertops and other upgrades. The 1st floor primary suite is a sanctuary of tranquility, featuring a luxurious en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. 3 additional bedrooms provide flexibility for a growing family or a home office. The backyard is fenced-in with a patio making it an ideal spot for entertaining or enjoying a quiet evening.  Go see today!!
